{"tid":294600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經]食嘢食到摺摺聲嘅人係咪應該拎去人道毀滅?","createTime":"2017-06-23T05:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T19:23:21.000Z","uid":76399,"like":109,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3279ffa11377efc92d498522a0cd323c9a95d5","tid":294600,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"次次同一班人食飯，其中總有一兩個人食嘢係食到摺摺/隻隻聲，嘈撚到仆街。<br />\n食到摺摺聲真係同啲豬食豬餿冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋點解依啲人唔會發現自己係同其他人唔同? <br />\n成枱食嘢勁靜嘅時候得你條撚樣可以食嘢食到其他枱都知你食緊嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲人係咪智商偏低先發覺唔到自己有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f754bda64c07212c71a0c2d55112ccaf3954525","tid":294600,"uid":67041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:59:57.000Z","msg":"enjoy your meal"},{"pid":"71c8e31d2d2d572bdfb8f30de1c869689db0ccbd","tid":294600,"uid":76399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"係咪啲低智商垃圾豬負皮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5cb7c2f8ce5ca98cc35c2a2967e1e08b7debde","tid":294600,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>enjoy your meal</blockquote><br />\nIf you have table manner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a509ec5afd03ed761dd34a4ae6f8926218365c0","tid":294600,"uid":16120,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/3ec739b9b894d3bc80760db7ca945c27/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F3ec739b9b894d3bc80760db7ca945c27%2Ftenor.gif&h=4c459524&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dc75b5370f7d4fa558e167d4cb581949afa6324","tid":294600,"uid":76399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017